    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "理解了，Approve返回EdgeNode表示任务重新激活。那InProgress主状态本身有哪些出口？我看到Pause到OnHold，Complete到Completed，还有Cancel。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "InProgress",
        "OnHold",
        "Pause",
        "Completed",
        "Complete",
        "Cancelled"
