    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，这三个出口都要。OnHold挂起状态内部需要区分Blocked和Deferred两种情况，分别对应MQTT Broker和Telemetry Stream的介入。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OnHold",
