      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "OnHold内部结构已添加：MQTT Broker关联Blocked，Telemetry Stream关联Deferred。恢复流转怎么设计？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OnHold",
